mutation CreateContactTemplateGof($inputArguments: CreateContactTemplateGoFParams!) {

    __typename

            ... on PlainTextField {

                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfSeconds
              }
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
            }
            ... on DateField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent

                valueEnum

              }
            }
            ... on DropdownField {
              fieldId

              description

              placeholderText

              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
            }
            ... on MultiSelectField {
              fieldId

              gofId

              description

              isRequired

              tooltip

                parentFieldId
                options
              }

            ... on CheckboxGroupField {
              fieldId

              name

              isRequired

              tooltip

              isDependent
              options
              defaultValues
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
            }
            ... on RadioGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
            }
            ... on PhoneNumberField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              isUnique
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
            }
            ... on FieldsSelectorField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
              dependentFields {
                option
                dependentFieldIds
              }
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
            }
          }
      category
    }
    ... on ContactTemplateNotFound {
      message
      contactTemplateId
    }
    ... on GoFNameAlreadyExists {
      message
      name
    }
    ... on UserIsNotAnAdministrator {
      message
    }
  }
}
